title: Memphis upsets No. 13 Ole Miss 37-24
text:
> Top News Memphis upsets No. 13 Ole Miss 37-24 Memphis head coach Justin Fuente, left, and Mississippi head coach Hugh Freeze watch players warm up before the start of an NCAA college football game Saturday, Oct. 17, 2015, in Memphis, Tenn. (AP Photo/Mark Humphrey)
